data.description: Move-in ready & motivated sellers! Almost 2 acres of quiet country living, 13 min from Hopkinsville, 40 min from Ft Campbell, and USDA 0% down payment eligible! Seller will give Buyers $5k towards closing costs! 4 bedroom, 2.5 baths, double oven, new dishwasher, heated floor in XL primary bath, tons of storage closets, washer/dryer included. Relax on your back deck, enjoy your extra large backyard (lot goes past treeline) with high producing blueberry bushes, plenty of plots for gardening, a small barn for goats, portable chicken pen, bonfire pit - your very own mini farm! Tons of play area for kids & pets. Ventless propane fireplace in living room can supplement HVAC for winter ambience and emergency heat. High speed internet via AT&T or HES. Detached 22'x28' (623 sf) two car garage with heat & electricity. Give yourself peaceful country living at an affordable price!
